headline: Is CME Group (CME) Pricing Look Stretched After Strong Multi Year Share Gains
summary: If you are looking at CME Group and wondering whether the recent price makes sense, you are not alone. This article walks through what that price could imply about value. CME Group last closed at US$279.50, with returns of 6.5% over the past 7 days, 3.9% over 30 days, 3.6% year to date, 22.4% over 1 year, 78.6% over 3 years, and 83.6% over 5 years, which gives plenty of data points for thinking about what investors may be pricing in.
